{"tid":1721860,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係冇覺好訓，至少我係","createTime":"2019-11-14T18:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T20:03:56.000Z","uid":305349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e1b8a1a9081c0a674e5fed99a967c70fe02ddb","tid":1721860,"uid":305349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:50:53.000Z","msg":"完全訓唔着&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日起碼一定要等到0500，<br />\n本樓豬十分期待《香港民主及人權法》既通過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過左五個月終於<span style=\"color: green;\">有機會有些小成果</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n受傷過、辛苦過、喊過、生命隕落過，<br />\n但咁多位巴絲既血汗、甚至生命係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對唔會白費</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驅除共黨，天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國佬咪撚出賣我地，出爾反爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時感覺香港人就自帶「被出賣」嘅<br />\n被動技能，好不安"},{"pid":"7e2ae16f00190043aba1030c7cd29ea77ac0cebd","tid":1721860,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e4b8724a640b774dd7ecb8e3c39702d1d4a98c","tid":1721860,"uid":275992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass